INSERT INTO `general_page` VALUES (1,0,'\n				<h5>Custom Application Development</h5>\n				<ul>\n					<li>We help you build the most complicated web application from the scratch in unbelievable brief amount of time!</li>\n					<li>We can also help you improve or migrate your present application on Grails and advise you how to improve your codeâ€™s quality. </li>\n				</ul>\n				<h5>CMS Platform</h5>\n				<p>We have developed and delivered several CMS (Content Management System) based applications. Based on clientâ€™s technology needs, we help identify the right CMS and customize and enhance the CMS for specific business needs.</p>\n				<h5>Open Source Consulting</h5>\n				<p>The company specializes in using latest open source and free tools and frameworks for software development. It helps its clients with the following:</p>\n				<ul >\n					<li>Migration to Linux platform</li>\n					<li>Evaluation of various open source tools/frameworks</li>\n					<li>Training on open source technologies.</li>\n				</ul>\n				<p>We generally prefer to implement most recent and latest application rather using old conventional tools of development. </p>\n				<h5>Training</h5>\n				<p>IntelliGrape offers a comprehensive catalog of training offerings on the following technology and agile methodology topics. </p>\n				<ul >\n					<li>Technology Training Catalogue\n						<ul >\n							<li>Introduction to Groovy</li>\n							<li>Introduction to Grails</li>\n							<li>Advanced Groovy</li>\n							<li>Advanced Grails</li>\n							<li>J2EE for Managers</li>\n							<li>Open Source Tools & Technologies</li>\n						</ul>\n					</li>\n					<li>Agile Methodologies Training Catalogue\n						<ul >\n							<li>Agile Workshop</li>\n							<li>Scrum for Team Members</li>\n							<li>Scrum for Managers</li>\n							<li>Introduction to Extreme Programming</li>\n						</ul>\n					</li>\n				</ul>','IntelliGrape Software is a web application/software development company in India. It is a leader in Groovy & Grails software development in India and follows Agile methodologies such as Scrum and Xtreme Programming (XP). IntelliGrape Software works only on open source tools and technologies.',': IntelliGrape Software :  India | Leaders in Groovy/Grails | Agile Methodologies | Open Source Tools | Offshore Software Development Company',4,'Our Services'),(2,0,'\n				<p>IntelliGrape follows Agile methodologies for software development. Scrum and XP Practices form an integral part of our development processes.</p>\n				<p>We broadly follow the following steps for application development. </p>\n				<ul class=\"arrow\">\n					<li>Comprehensive and detailed analysis of the business needs.</li>\n					<li>Segregation of requirements into small modules/iterations as per priority.</li>\n					<li>Initiate design concept &amp; programming on iterations.</li>\n					<li>Client feedback on completion of each iteration.</li>\n					<li>Block wise testing of application to get the real time feedback.</li>\n					<li>Practicing Scrum and XP principals such as re-factoring, pair programming to eliminate redundancies and optimize efficiency. </li>\n				</ul>\n				<h5>Our core philosophy for web application development</h5>\n				<p class=\"bold\">Two-Way Communication</p>\n				<p>Though sounding rude, but we DO NOT want to work with a client who does not feel the need of clear communication. We believe in having a clear and two-way communication. We do not believe in having a guarded communication with our clients. We do not hesitate in sharing our problems/roadblocks with the client and prefer to give an honest and clear picture to the client. On the other hand, we also expect our client to elucidate the requirements as clearly as possible and provide us the feedback almost instantly.</p>\n				<p class=\"bold\">Flexible Approach and Mind-Set</p>\n				<p>Though we expect the client to lay down the requirements clearly, but also know the fact that it is practically impossible to not to digress from the original requirement. By virtue of Agile delivery model, we are able to respond to business change quickly. Agile processes give us an edge, particularly for new application development where the detailed requirements are unclear or likely to change with time. </p>\n				<p class=\"bold\">Small Iterations of 1-6 weeks</p>\n				<p>We apply time bound iterative and evolutionary development. Small iterations from 1-6 weeks, depending on the kind of application to be developed, are delivered to the client.</p>\n				<p><img class=\"image\" alt=\"Intelligrape work\" src=\"images/work1.gif\"></p>\n				<p class=\"bold\">Track of Project Status</p>\n				<p>Our team conducts daily stand up meetings to provide the updates on the completed tasks and activities on daily basis. We track the status of project almost on hourly basis. An effective burn-down chart tracks both the amount of work required to implement a particular iteration and the work needed to complete the entire project. </p>\n				<p class=\"bold\">Automated Functional Testing</p>\n				<p>We are quite religious about automated unit/integration/functional testing.</p>\n				<p><img class=\"image\" alt=\"Intelligrape work\" src=\"images/work2.gif\"></p>   \n        ','IntelliGrape Software is a web application/software development company in India. It is a leader in Groovy & Grails software development in India and follows Agile methodologies such as Scrum and Xtreme Programming (XP). IntelliGrape Software works only on open source tools and technologies.',': IntelliGrape Software :  India | Leaders in Groovy/Grails | Agile Methodologies | Open Source Tools | Offshore Software Development Company',10,'Company - How we Work'),(3,0,'\n				<h5>Grails Leader</h5>\n				<p>If you want an application to be developed on Groovy/Grails, then WE are the company you might be looking for. We are ONLY focused on Grails and knows the ins-outs of the technology.</p>\n				<h5>Highly Energetic and Productive Team</h5>\n				<p>We do not have any Project Manager in our team. The ONLY thing that is respected in IntelliGrape is love for technology. Our Team members</p>\n				<ul class=\"arrow\">\n					<li>are PASSIONATE GRAILS DEVELOPERS.</li>\n					<li>are all Agile practioners.</li>\n					<li>are Open Source Enthusiats.</li>\n					<li>are contributor to Grails mailing list.</li>\n					<li>are active Bloggers. www.intelligrape.com/blog</li>\n					<li>possess domain experience in Online Marketing, Publication Industry, Pharma Industry, Finance and Telecom.</li>\n				</ul>\n				<h5>Close collaboration with clients </h5>\n				<p>We try to collaborate very closely with the client. We believe in early feedback, small iterations and frequent releases. Also, since we are ONLY focused on Grails development, we do not take any project that comes our way. We scrutinize the project and its fitment to our strengths and then take up the project.</p>\n				<h5>Proven Results/Satisfied Clients </h5>\n				<p>We have delivered/deployed quite a few applications on Grails which are pretty stable, and running successfully. Our clients have been highly satisfied with our understanding, knowledge, communication and delivery.</p>\n				<h5>Quality of code</h5>\n				<p>We have a mind-set of writing neat and clean code. We DO NOT have any hesitation in sharing our code quality with you.  We can also send you the code that we have written for already deployed applications.</p>\n				<h5>Code Camps</h5>\n				<p>Learning is not a process in IntelliGrape. It is the culture. Once in every fort-night, the entire company gets together for an intensive knowledge transfer and presentation program. We organize presentations, brainstorming sessions, hands-on sessions and review cycles. 1 or 2 team members pick any topic, generally related to present projects or new technology and present that to all other team members. </p>\n        ','IntelliGrape Software is a web application/software development company in India. It is a leader in Groovy & Grails software development in India and follows Agile methodologies such as Scrum and Xtreme Programming (XP). IntelliGrape Software works only on open source tools and technologies.',': IntelliGrape Software :  India | Leaders in Groovy/Grails | Agile Methodologies | Open Source Tools | Offshore Software Development Company',5,'Why Us?'),(4,0,'\n				                            <p>We currently work only on Groovy and Grails. We also have experience working with JEE on number of commercial projects. </p>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">RAD Tools:</span> We possess expertise level knowledge on Grails. We are active contributor to Grails mailing list and Grails Blogs.</p>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Scripting Language: </span>Groovy</p>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Operating System: </span>We have experience on almost all the Operating Systems in vogue but we strongly prefer to work on Unix (Solaris) and Linux (Ubuntu). </p>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Databases:</span> We provide various options on database to the customer as per their requirements and production environment details.</p>\n				                            <p>We are pretty flexible and comfortable with any other database if our client wishes so but we prefer to work on the below mentioned databases.</p>\n				                            <ul class=\"arrow\">\n					                            <li>Oracle (PL/SQL)</li>\n					                            <li>MySQL</li>\n					                            <li>PostgreSQL</li>\n					                            <li>SQL Server</li>\n				                            </ul>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Frameworks :</span> We work on light weight frameworks such as</p>\n				                            <ul class=\"arrow\">\n					                            <li>Hibernate</li>\n					                            <li>Spring</li>\n				                            </ul>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Testing Environment:</span> The environment consists of separate servers for deployment of demo or testing versions with dedicated resource to assist on network/connectivity and infrastructure related issues.</p>\n				                            <p>The updated versions of the developed applications are regularly deployed on the testing server which is utilized for internal as well as client testing. </p>\n				                            <p>We use the following automated testing tools: </p>\n				                            <ul class=\"arrow\">\n					                            <li>Selenium</li>\n					                            <li>Mercury </li>\n					                            <li>Fitnesse</li>\n					                            <li>Jmeter</li>\n					                            <li>Canoo WebTest</li>\n				                            </ul>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Integrated Development Environment:</span>We use the following IDE to increase our productivity</p>\n				                            <ul class=\"arrow\">\n					                            <li>Eclipse</li>\n					                            <li>IntelliJ</li>\n				                            </ul>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">AJAX Frameworks : </span>We use the following  AJAX  Frameworks</p>\n				                            <ul class=\"arrow\">\n					                            <li>DOJO</li>\n					                            <li>DWR</li>\n					                            <li>JQuery</li>\n				                            </ul>\n				                            <p><span class=\"bold\">Deployment and Maintenance : </span>We have deployed number of grails applications over  Linux, Windows, Mac OS, Sun Solaris, CentOS </p>\n			                        ','IntelliGrape Software is a web application/software development company in India. It is a leader in Groovy & Grails software development in India and follows Agile methodologies such as Scrum and Xtreme Programming (XP). IntelliGrape Software works only on open source tools and technologies.',': IntelliGrape Software :  India | Leaders in Groovy/Grails | Agile Methodologies | Open Source Tools | Offshore Software Development Company',9,'Company - Our Tool-Kit');
